[SetUp "1"]

26. Kg2 { Can you find the most forcing continuation here? } 26... h4
{ Maybe not objectively the best, but it forces a very unpleasant endgame where White will suffer.   26...a5  27.Bf1  a4  is also very good for Black but it is way less forcing. }
27. Qxh4 Qe5 28. Qf4
{ In the next exercise we'll see why  28.Bf1  is not a good idea. } 28... Qxf4
29. gxf4 Nh5 30. Bf1 Nxf4+
{ Black has the more active pieces and a superior endgame. } *

