6. f4
{ A very unusual setup by White. It is extremely rare to put the bishop on g5 and then follow up with the four pawns setup. How would you react? }
6... c5
{ In almost all Kings Indian's it is important to strike at the center with either c5 or e5 and seeing as e5 is almost impossible, c5 makes a lot of sense.   6...e5?  7.dxe5  dxe5  8.Qxd8  Rxd8  9.fxe5+-  Simply loses a piece. }
*

