27. Rg1
{ This position is taken out of a sideline on move 16. It perfectly illustrates the attacking potential of the KID. How does Black win here? }
27... Nxh3 28. gxh3 g2+
{ It's over for White. If  29.Kh2  then  29...Qg5  threatening  30.--  Qg3+  31.Qxg3  fxg3  . }
