31. Kf2 { Finish White off! } 31... e3+ 32. Bxe3 { Or  32.Ke1  Bc3+  . } 32...
fxe3+ 33. Kxe3 Nxf1+ { 33...Qh4  also wins. } 34. Bxf1 Qg1+
{ White's king is completely exposed and it is only a matter of time until he gets mated. }
