40. Ba4 Nc3 41. Rxd4 exd4 42. Bb3 d2
{ A possible continuation would be  43.a4  Be3+  44.Kf1  d3  45.b5  Ne2-+  and @@StartFEN@@8/p7/5ppk/8/PP5p/1BnpbP1P/3p2P1/R4K2 w - - 0 45@@EndFEN@@  45.Bd1  Kg5  46.b5  Bd4  when White cannot push the pawns further up the board. }
