51. Nc2
{ White tries to activate his knight but falls victim to a simple tactic. }
51... fxe4 52. fxe4 Nxe4 53. Nxe4 Qxd5+ 54. Kb2 Qxe4
{ Two connected passers should be enough to win the game. } *

