[SetUp "1"]

32. c5 { White just pushed his passed c-pawn. What did he miss? } 32... Rd1+
33. Kh2 Qf4+ { This check forces White to make a huge concession. } 34. g3
{ 34.Rg3  34...Rd3! } 34... Qf1
{ Threatening mate on g1 and h1 as well as attacking the rook on b5.  Instead,  34...Qxe3  35.Qb3+  loses the rook on d1 and makes things really complicated. }
35. Qg2 Qxb5 *

