[Black "FairChess_on_YouTube vs. Hikaru, Online Blitz 2019"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r4rk1/1pp3bp/n2p2p1/p1nPp3/2P3Pq/P1N1B2P/1PQ1NP2/R3K2R w KQ - 0 15"]
[SetUp "1"]

15. O-O-O
{ White is hoping that he will be the one playing on the kingside. Can you prove him wrong? }
15... Bh6
{ Completely destabilizes White's entire kingside.  16.--  Rxf2  is already a threat. }
16. Kb1 Bxe3 17. fxe3 Rf3
{ Black is not only winning a pawn, but has also full control over the kingside. }
*

