40... Qf5 41. g4
{ Opening the g-file with  41.gxf4  gxf4  is fatal. White has to give material to prevent mate, but the position remains overwhelming. Stockfish already announces mate in 18:   A@@EndBracket@@ @@StartFEN@@r6k/8/1p1p4/3Ppq1p/1PQ1Rp2/5P1P/r7/1R3NK1 w - - 0 42@@EndFEN@@  42.Nh2  Qg6+  43.Ng4  hxg4  and now capturing with the h-pawn would open the h-file for the black queen while capturing with the f-pawn allows Black's rook to infiltrate via the third rank with ...Ra3. However, if he doesn't recapture the pawn, Black can open the g-file... it is hopeless.   B@@EndBracket@@ @@StartFEN@@r6k/8/1p1p4/3Ppq1p/1PQ1Rp2/5P1P/r7/1R3NK1 w - - 0 42@@EndFEN@@  42.Re2  Rxe2  43.Qxe2  Qxb1  wins material and Black continues his mating attack. }
